  "body": "Currently py-evm doesn't have a standard place to store its configs and chain data. We need to agree on one and start storing stuff there to avoid having to hard-code or [regenerate values on every run](https://github.com/ethereum/py-evm/pull/189#discussion_r154775751)\r\n\r\nI believe we should use $XDG_DATA_HOME and $XDG_CONFIG_HOME as per https://specifications.freedesktop.org/basedir-spec/basedir-spec-latest.html ",
